1
00:01:35,170 --> 00:01:36,600
<i>[Scarlet Heart 2]</i>

2
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:43,060
<i>[Episode 23]</i>

3
00:01:45,642 --> 00:01:47,684
If you sleep here tonight,

4
00:01:47,684 --> 00:01:50,334
will your mom suspect us?

5
00:01:51,851 --> 00:01:53,475
What would she suspect?

6
00:01:53,475 --> 00:01:57,518
We used to sleep together when we were in college.

7
00:01:58,726 --> 00:02:02,575
I'm worried she might find out you're hiding something from her.

8
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:08,684
She's so busy.

9
00:02:08,684 --> 00:02:10,600
She doesn't have time to worry about me.

10
00:02:14,559 --> 00:02:16,709
That's what you think.

11
00:02:17,642 --> 00:02:20,892
But you actually can't hide anything from your parents.

12
00:02:20,892 --> 00:02:23,175
They know their children the most.

13
00:02:33,283 --> 00:02:37,400
Do you know why I'm keeping this baby?

14
00:02:42,309 --> 00:02:43,725
Why?

15
00:02:44,684 --> 00:02:47,434
Before my mom had me,

16
00:02:47,434 --> 00:02:50,510
she was pregnant before.

17
00:02:51,475 --> 00:02:53,809
But they were not married at the time,

18
00:02:56,309 --> 00:02:58,917
so my father asked her to get an abortion.

19
00:03:00,475 --> 00:03:02,783
She had no choice but to do it.

20
00:03:04,434 --> 00:03:07,017
After she came back, she changed.

21
00:03:09,767 --> 00:03:12,934
I don't want to be like her.

22
00:03:12,934 --> 00:03:16,292
She'll always have a scar on her heart that will never recover.

23
00:03:17,976 --> 00:03:19,809
So because of that,

24
00:03:21,250 --> 00:03:23,760
you want this baby to be born?

25
00:03:26,892 --> 00:03:28,520
Piggy.

26
00:03:29,590 --> 00:03:31,530
Stop laugh at me.

27
00:03:34,392 --> 00:03:39,080
I want to be a perfect mother.

28
00:03:42,309 --> 00:03:44,959
Before I came back,

29
00:03:44,959 --> 00:03:48,200
I enrolled in many parenting classes.

30
00:03:49,684 --> 00:03:52,767
Do you know that feeling

31
00:03:52,767 --> 00:03:55,480
of getting to go to class with my baby?

32
00:03:56,099 --> 00:03:58,530
It feels so amazing.

33
00:04:00,099 --> 00:04:02,626
I have so much pride.

34
00:04:02,626 --> 00:04:04,742
I never imagined

35
00:04:04,742 --> 00:04:07,167
that it would bring me so much motivation and courage

36
00:04:07,167 --> 00:04:09,534
to prompt me to come back to find Sihan.

37
00:04:20,159 --> 00:04:22,800
I want to give him a home.

38
00:04:27,242 --> 00:04:28,899
What are you crying?

39
00:04:32,267 --> 00:04:34,434
I'm so touched.

40
00:04:42,142 --> 00:04:44,417
I'm scared.

41
00:04:44,417 --> 00:04:47,142
I don't want him to be like my father.

42
00:04:47,142 --> 00:04:48,659
No, he won't.

43
00:04:51,309 --> 00:04:53,851
If he is like your father,

44
00:04:56,684 --> 00:04:58,860
I will definitely support you.

45
00:05:31,225 --> 00:05:34,459
Xiaoxiao, listen to me.

46
00:05:34,459 --> 00:05:36,100
I thought about everything.

47
00:05:36,100 --> 00:05:38,620
I'm giving up everything and choosing you.

48
00:05:42,684 --> 00:05:45,199
I don't understand what you're saying.

49
00:05:45,199 --> 00:05:46,650
I'm sorry, Director Kang. I'm running late

50
00:05:46,650 --> 00:05:48,792
Xiaoxiao.

51
00:05:49,517 --> 00:05:50,475
Let's leave.

52
00:05:50,475 --> 00:05:52,620
Let's leave this place.

53
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:57,934
This is your decision,

54
00:05:58,851 --> 00:06:00,667
not my decision.

55
00:06:01,225 --> 00:06:03,592
I handed in my resignation.

56
00:06:11,809 --> 00:06:14,100
It can't solve your problem.

57
00:06:15,834 --> 00:06:18,325
I don't want anything.

58
00:06:18,325 --> 00:06:20,042
I just want you.

59
00:06:22,726 --> 00:06:24,475
We can't be together.

60
00:06:24,475 --> 00:06:27,225
Let me prove to you that nothing's impossible.

61
00:06:27,225 --> 00:06:28,492
We can't be together.

62
00:06:28,492 --> 00:06:29,934
Why don't you understand?

63
00:06:29,934 --> 00:06:31,018
I don't understand.

64
00:06:31,018 --> 00:06:32,283
You still love me.

65
00:06:32,283 --> 00:06:33,918
Why are you doing this?

66
00:06:33,918 --> 00:06:37,409
♫ <i>Light comes after dark</i>♫

67
00:06:37,409 --> 00:06:40,992
♫ <i>Only then can I see the faint existence of you</i> ♫

68
00:06:40,992 --> 00:06:46,375
♫ <i>I was just like the star that is far apart from you</i> ♫

69
00:06:46,375 --> 00:06:47,742
Xiaoxiao.

70
00:06:48,517 --> 00:06:49,475
Xiaoxiao.

71
00:06:49,475 --> 00:06:51,809
Let go of me.

72
00:06:51,809 --> 00:06:53,325
I've made my decision.

73
00:06:53,325 --> 00:06:55,067
No one can change my mind.

74
00:06:55,809 --> 00:06:58,000
Xinyi can change your mind.

75
00:06:58,767 --> 00:07:01,459
I've already sent her a message this morning.

76
00:07:01,459 --> 00:07:03,367
I told her everything.

77
00:07:10,350 --> 00:07:11,942
What did you say?

78
00:07:14,100 --> 00:07:15,767
Say it again.

79
00:07:17,375 --> 00:07:19,590
I've sent her a message

80
00:07:20,225 --> 00:07:22,726
and told her everything.

81
00:07:22,726 --> 00:07:24,999
Are you crazy?

82
00:07:24,999 --> 00:07:26,484
Xiaoxiao.

83
00:07:27,392 --> 00:07:28,892
Xinyi.

84
00:07:30,267 --> 00:07:32,690
Xinyi is pregnant.

85
00:07:33,475 --> 00:07:34,751
She is pregnant with your child.

86
00:07:34,751 --> 00:07:41,851
♫ <i>My love is like dust, scattered in the border zone</i> ♫

87
00:07:41,851 --> 00:07:48,992
♫ <i>No longer expecting anything from anyone, is this considered freedom?</i>♫

88
00:07:48,992 --> 00:07:55,959
♫ <i>A promise is like dust, constantly being buried in time</i> ♫

89
00:07:55,959 --> 00:08:06,617
♫ <i>Who stills remember the confession made in heavy rain? ♫</i>

90
00:08:12,584 --> 00:08:13,718
Princess.

91
00:08:13,718 --> 00:08:15,325
Piggy.

92
00:08:16,183 --> 00:08:17,659
I left my phone at your home.

93
00:08:17,659 --> 00:08:20,099
Can you bring it to me?

94
00:08:20,099 --> 00:08:21,659
I still have a meeting this morning.

95
00:08:21,659 --> 00:08:24,192
All my details are in my phone.

96
00:08:24,192 --> 00:08:31,325
♫ <i>My love is like dust, scattered in the border zone</i> ♫

97
00:08:31,325 --> 00:08:33,409
♫ <i>No longer expecting anything from anyone, is this considered freedom?</i>♫

98
00:08:33,409 --> 00:08:36,925
Okay, I'll bring it to you.

99
00:08:37,642 --> 00:08:39,267
Thank you.

100
00:08:39,267 --> 00:08:42,284
You're welcome. Goodbye.

101
00:08:45,367 --> 00:08:52,325
♫ <i>Who stills remember the confession made in heavy rain? ♫</i>

102
00:08:52,325 --> 00:08:55,009
You almost ruined it for everyone.

103
00:09:10,099 --> 00:09:13,026
Do you know why she didn't tell you about the pregnancy?

104
00:09:18,709 --> 00:09:21,183
She doesn't want to pressure you.

105
00:09:21,183 --> 00:09:23,709
She doesn't want to force you to marry her.

106
00:09:24,309 --> 00:09:28,509
She wants you to love her again through her own efforts.

107
00:09:31,851 --> 00:09:34,209
She really loves you.

108
00:09:42,559 --> 00:09:44,509
Say something, will you?

109
00:09:49,283 --> 00:09:51,117
What do you want me to say?

110
00:09:53,225 --> 00:09:55,142
Tell me what your plan is.

111
00:10:00,559 --> 00:10:02,626
What do you want me to do?

112
00:10:02,626 --> 00:10:04,876
It's not about me now.

113
00:10:05,434 --> 00:10:07,384
It's what you should do.

114
00:10:08,409 --> 00:10:10,892
Don't you think you should be responsible to Xinyi?

115
00:10:12,283 --> 00:10:15,559
Do you think this responsibility can bring happiness to her?

116
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:17,950
There's no happiness without responsibility either.

117
00:10:18,892 --> 00:10:21,600
Do you want your kids to be like you

118
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:23,742
and never have a father-figure?

119
00:10:24,517 --> 00:10:25,542
No, I...

120
00:10:25,542 --> 00:10:28,292
Xinyi needs protection.

121
00:10:30,050 --> 00:10:32,680
She needs you.

122
00:10:34,475 --> 00:10:36,570
Xinyi can't lose you.

123
00:10:39,892 --> 00:10:42,042
Then what about us?

124
00:10:48,209 --> 00:10:49,992
Let's just let our relationship

125
00:10:53,059 --> 00:10:55,540
become a secret forever.

126
00:11:07,684 --> 00:11:10,300
That's our ending?

127
00:11:12,959 --> 00:11:15,099
An hour ago,

128
00:11:15,876 --> 00:11:20,234
I wanted to grab your hand and run away.

129
00:11:21,934 --> 00:11:24,767
One hour later, you're telling me

130
00:11:26,976 --> 00:11:29,680
to let it be our secret forever.

131
00:11:33,100 --> 00:11:36,309
Our love just vanished in the air.

132
00:11:42,434 --> 00:11:43,999
I'm sorry.

133
00:11:46,726 --> 00:11:48,618
This is my decision.

134
00:11:50,142 --> 00:11:54,800
It hasn't been easy for me either.

135
00:11:56,834 --> 00:11:58,751
I know my decision

136
00:12:00,142 --> 00:12:02,726
has hurt you deeply,

137
00:12:02,726 --> 00:12:04,999
and hurt me as well.

138
00:12:06,559 --> 00:12:08,880
But compared to what Xinyi is going through,

139
00:12:09,809 --> 00:12:12,542
this is nothing.

140
00:12:15,059 --> 00:12:16,975
This is what I've decided.

141
00:12:34,434 --> 00:12:36,099
Sihan.

142
00:12:36,099 --> 00:12:39,610
What is the matter?

143
00:12:45,350 --> 00:12:47,684
Stop looking at me like that.

144
00:12:47,684 --> 00:12:50,520
I'm confused.

145
00:12:53,851 --> 00:12:55,220
Xinyi.

146
00:12:56,092 --> 00:12:59,260
When did you find out you were pregnant?

147
00:13:00,851 --> 00:13:02,090
You...

148
00:13:02,700 --> 00:13:04,750
How do you know?

149
00:13:05,976 --> 00:13:08,130
That's not important.

150
00:13:08,130 --> 00:13:12,850
I just want to know when you found out.

151
00:13:16,142 --> 00:13:18,250
About a month ago.

152
00:13:19,884 --> 00:13:21,700
How old is the baby now?

153
00:13:24,434 --> 00:13:26,270
Four months.

154
00:13:34,059 --> 00:13:36,440
Why didn't you tell me?

155
00:13:37,267 --> 00:13:39,183
I don't want to burden you,

156
00:13:39,183 --> 00:13:41,910
and I don't want to force you to marry me.

157
00:13:43,559 --> 00:13:46,050
Don't I have burden now?

158
00:13:47,225 --> 00:13:48,800
Sihan.

159
00:13:49,575 --> 00:13:51,826
I know we have a barrier,

160
00:13:51,826 --> 00:13:53,517
but I don't want to depend on the baby.

161
00:13:53,517 --> 00:13:56,800
I think want to depend on myself to let you fall in love with me again.

162
00:14:01,767 --> 00:14:03,280
Xinyi.

163
00:14:04,459 --> 00:14:07,250
What do you plan to do with the baby?

164
00:14:09,059 --> 00:14:10,590
What?

165
00:14:13,334 --> 00:14:16,525
I mean how are you going to handle this?

166
00:14:21,475 --> 00:14:23,080
Handle?

167
00:14:25,626 --> 00:14:27,809
He is a living being.

168
00:14:27,809 --> 00:14:30,100
He is our child.

169
00:14:33,200 --> 00:14:35,350
I am his mother.

170
00:14:35,350 --> 00:14:37,851
I'm going to have this baby.

171
00:14:37,851 --> 00:14:41,584
He's not an object.

172
00:14:43,076 --> 00:14:45,309
Xinyi, listen to me.

173
00:14:45,309 --> 00:14:47,809
The baby is just four months.

174
00:14:47,809 --> 00:14:49,860
There's still time for an abortion.

175
00:14:51,309 --> 00:14:52,617
I'm sorry, Sihan.

176
00:14:52,617 --> 00:14:54,626
I have nothing to say.

177
00:14:54,626 --> 00:14:57,250
Xinyi.

178
00:14:58,159 --> 00:14:59,375
Xinyi.

179
00:15:00,059 --> 00:15:02,450
Xinyi, I'm sorry.

180
00:15:02,450 --> 00:15:04,517
I'm not ready to be a father yet.

181
00:15:04,517 --> 00:15:05,934
Please abort the baby.

182
00:15:05,934 --> 00:15:08,099
I hope you can understand.

183
00:15:08,099 --> 00:15:09,742
I don't understand.

184
00:15:09,742 --> 00:15:11,042
I cannot understand.

185
00:15:11,042 --> 00:15:12,642
Xinyi.

186
00:15:12,642 --> 00:15:15,367
We are not husband and wife, and we are not couple.

187
00:15:15,367 --> 00:15:18,383
If the baby is born, how could he accept his life?

188
00:15:20,434 --> 00:15:23,559
Sihan, I get it.

189
00:15:23,559 --> 00:15:26,759
You must have your reasons for saying this to me.

190
00:15:30,492 --> 00:15:34,267
I'm sorry, I'm very sorry.

191
00:15:34,267 --> 00:15:36,851
I don't want your apologies.

192
00:15:36,851 --> 00:15:38,183
Xin...

193
00:15:41,475 --> 00:15:42,875
Zhuo Yue.

194
00:15:42,875 --> 00:15:45,584
Book me on tomorrow evening's flight.

195
00:15:46,700 --> 00:15:48,100
I can go anywhere.

196
00:15:48,100 --> 00:15:50,559
I just want to leave this place.

197
00:15:50,559 --> 00:15:52,592
It's best that I can go overseas.

198
00:15:54,659 --> 00:15:58,500
Okay, book me the ticket to Thailand.

199
00:15:58,500 --> 00:15:59,920
Thank you.

200
00:16:18,392 --> 00:16:20,684
I've looked at the resignation letter.

201
00:16:20,684 --> 00:16:24,967
There's nothing good in this aside from your writing style.

202
00:16:26,209 --> 00:16:28,600
I don't need your appraisal,

203
00:16:28,600 --> 00:16:30,659
I need your approval.

204
00:16:31,434 --> 00:16:35,684
When can you start to be more understanding?

205
00:16:35,684 --> 00:16:37,600
What is it?

206
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:39,309
You are my son.

207
00:16:39,309 --> 00:16:41,959
You are the eldest in our family.

208
00:16:41,959 --> 00:16:44,240
Do you know what that means?

209
00:16:45,350 --> 00:16:48,350
Let me tell you.

210
00:16:48,350 --> 00:16:53,034
It means that you are the future man of the house.

211
00:16:53,684 --> 00:16:56,976
Zhen Tian Group is our family business.

212
00:16:56,976 --> 00:16:58,392
You're the successor.

213
00:16:58,392 --> 00:17:01,559
Your resignation means your betrayal to the family.

214
00:17:01,559 --> 00:17:04,440
So I cannot accept your resignation.

215
00:17:06,876 --> 00:17:08,559
Whether you accept it or not,

216
00:17:08,559 --> 00:17:10,792
I really want to leave.

217
00:17:12,183 --> 00:17:15,576
I know you've been having some issues in your relationship.

218
00:17:16,767 --> 00:17:20,583
I can give you two days leave to let you clear up your issue.

219
00:17:25,475 --> 00:17:26,918
Chairman.

220
00:17:29,059 --> 00:17:31,099
Director Kang, I've booked the ticket.

221
00:17:31,099 --> 00:17:32,940
10 o'clock tonight.

222
00:17:32,940 --> 00:17:34,250
Here's your passport.

223
00:18:04,642 --> 00:18:11,142
♫ <i>The whole room is empty</i> ♫

224
00:18:11,142 --> 00:18:16,750
♫ <i>Even if you are here, right beside me</i> ♫

225
00:18:18,267 --> 00:18:21,820
♫ <i>The window that was ajar</i> ♫

226
00:18:21,820 --> 00:18:25,200
♫ <i>The dim glow of light</i> ♫

227
00:18:25,209 --> 00:18:27,809
♫ <i>They couldn't light up the darkness in your heart</i> ♫

228
00:18:27,809 --> 00:18:31,959
♫ <i>I couldn't forgive you</i> ♫

229
00:18:33,726 --> 00:18:40,434
♫ <i>I gave you everything I had</i> ♫

230
00:18:41,450 --> 00:18:43,392
You're here.

231
00:18:43,392 --> 00:18:45,050
A glass of whiskey.

232
00:18:47,309 --> 00:18:54,018
♫ <i>Perhaps letting go of the entanglements will help clear the mind</i> ♫

233
00:18:54,018 --> 00:18:55,317
Another.

234
00:19:01,434 --> 00:19:05,026
♫ <i>Love is not related to kindness</i> ♫

235
00:19:06,325 --> 00:19:07,609
Another.

236
00:19:08,684 --> 00:19:13,183
♫ <i>Unfortunately, we have tons of desire</i> ♫

237
00:19:13,183 --> 00:19:15,934
♫ <i>Turning love into aggressiveness</i> ♫

238
00:19:15,934 --> 00:19:19,542
♫ <i>Hatred is not related to kindness</i> ♫

239
00:19:19,542 --> 00:19:23,600
♫ <i>It doesn't matter who has greater courage</i> ♫

240
00:19:23,600 --> 00:19:28,500
♫ <i>The pain still exists because of the longing memories</i> ♫

241
00:19:28,500 --> 00:19:30,600
It's the third glass.

242
00:19:34,959 --> 00:19:39,600
A mature man shouldn't come to a boy's bar to get drunk.

243
00:19:41,367 --> 00:19:43,476
You're still mad at me.

244
00:19:44,392 --> 00:19:47,559
Seems like I touched a sore spot that day.

245
00:19:47,559 --> 00:19:49,517
What is your sore spot?

246
00:19:49,517 --> 00:19:52,625
Meng Xinyi or Zhang Xiao?

247
00:19:59,100 --> 00:20:01,309
When you button your clothes,

248
00:20:01,309 --> 00:20:04,018
you already buttoned the first one wrong.

249
00:20:04,018 --> 00:20:06,459
You didn't realize until the last button.

250
00:20:09,934 --> 00:20:12,467
A lot of things have been wrong from the start.

251
00:20:13,684 --> 00:20:16,959
You can unbutton and re-button.

252
00:20:16,959 --> 00:20:20,892
But there are some things that you can't start over.

253
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:25,350
Only one person can untie the dead knot here.

254
00:20:26,309 --> 00:20:28,125
That person is you.

255
00:20:37,083 --> 00:20:40,392
Princess, don't cry.

256
00:20:40,392 --> 00:20:41,517
What is going on?

257
00:20:41,517 --> 00:20:44,225
Just tell me, will you?

258
00:20:44,225 --> 00:20:47,350
He is so cruel.

259
00:20:47,350 --> 00:20:50,326
Cruel like my father.

260
00:20:51,434 --> 00:20:53,083
Director Kang?

261
00:20:54,667 --> 00:20:58,851
Yes, he doesn't want the baby.

262
00:20:58,851 --> 00:21:02,434
He doesn't want our baby.

263
00:21:02,434 --> 00:21:04,099
That's impossible.

264
00:21:04,099 --> 00:21:06,184
There must be some misunderstanding.

265
00:21:07,100 --> 00:21:11,634
He said it, he said it so calmly.

266
00:21:16,892 --> 00:21:20,559
Princess, go back and rest.

267
00:21:20,559 --> 00:21:22,809
It's not good for you or the baby

268
00:21:22,809 --> 00:21:25,084
to be like this.

269
00:21:28,726 --> 00:21:31,059
Piggy.

270
00:21:31,059 --> 00:21:34,150
Did you tell him?

271
00:21:34,767 --> 00:21:38,242
