00:41:07,076 --> 00:41:08,642
Okay.

550
00:41:08,642 --> 00:41:11,000
Hold this, I'll go try them.

551
00:41:13,434 --> 00:41:16,267
Princess, do you need help?

552
00:41:16,267 --> 00:41:18,100
No, thanks.

553
00:41:18,100 --> 00:41:19,459
Okay.

554
00:41:27,767 --> 00:41:28,742
Look.

555
00:41:28,742 --> 00:41:31,292
The plane to Indonesia today crashed.

556
00:41:31,292 --> 00:41:33,684
Do you think I should call the travel agency?

557
00:41:33,684 --> 00:41:35,475
It's so dangerous now.

558
00:41:35,475 --> 00:41:39,000
I think I should just stay at home.

559
00:41:39,000 --> 00:41:40,367
Yes.

560
00:41:42,350 --> 00:41:43,851
What were you saying?

561
00:41:43,851 --> 00:41:45,283
No, we didn't say anything.

562
00:41:45,283 --> 00:41:47,034
About some plane crash.

563
00:41:47,034 --> 00:41:49,100
Yes, the plane flying to Indonesia crashed.

564
00:41:49,100 --> 00:41:50,767
They were forced to land.

565
00:41:50,767 --> 00:41:52,283
Check your Weibo.

566
00:41:57,492 --> 00:41:58,892
Piggy.

567
00:41:59,475 --> 00:42:00,242
What is it?

568
00:42:00,242 --> 00:42:02,934
Something happened to Sihan.

569
00:42:02,934 --> 00:42:04,826
Miss, the gown.

570
00:42:07,325 --> 00:42:08,800
Sihan.

571
00:42:09,809 --> 00:42:13,076
Sihan, you're safe.

572
00:42:13,076 --> 00:42:14,375
You were not on the plane.

573
00:42:14,375 --> 00:42:16,120
Thank God!

574
00:42:16,809 --> 00:42:19,617
<i>Luckily it's just a false alarm.</i>

575
00:42:19,617 --> 00:42:22,559
<i>Xinyi loves Sihan with her whole heart.</i>

576
00:42:22,559 --> 00:42:28,042
<i>I understand that I have to go back to my life.</i>

577
00:42:28,042 --> 00:42:31,517
Sister, I didn't come here to learn to clean the floor.

578
00:42:31,517 --> 00:42:32,767
Why are you asking me to do this?

579
00:42:32,767 --> 00:42:34,099
Stop grumbling.

580
00:42:34,099 --> 00:42:36,050
Do you want to learn to make cocktails?

581
00:42:38,225 --> 00:42:40,242
Do you have stronger alcohol?

582
00:42:43,267 --> 00:42:45,867
Xiaoxiao, why are you here?

583
00:42:45,867 --> 00:42:49,350
My boss set a rule that girls cannot order spirits.

584
00:42:49,350 --> 00:42:52,183
I will have to ask my boss.

585
00:42:52,183 --> 00:42:53,784
Boss said no.

586
00:42:55,309 --> 00:42:57,425
Drinking isn't a good release.

587
00:42:57,425 --> 00:42:59,100
Follow me.

588
00:42:59,100 --> 00:43:00,792
Where are we going?

589
00:43:02,892 --> 00:43:05,059
She's gone again.

590
00:43:05,059 --> 00:43:07,018
Give me a beer.

591
00:43:07,018 --> 00:43:09,420
What beer? Drink this.

592
00:43:09,420 --> 00:43:11,100
It's not as strong as a beer.

593
00:43:11,100 --> 00:43:14,059
Yes. And you won't smell funny.

594
00:43:27,059 --> 00:43:29,099
Stop interfering.

595
00:43:29,099 --> 00:43:30,767
Leave me alone.

596
00:43:30,767 --> 00:43:32,617
They are getting married.

597
00:43:32,617 --> 00:43:34,883
Black Cat Detective does not exist anymore.

598
00:43:36,059 --> 00:43:40,099
I just want to let you know that you have many friends.

599
00:43:40,934 --> 00:43:43,300
And me.

600
00:43:43,300 --> 00:43:45,099
As long as you're willing to let us in,

601
00:43:45,099 --> 00:43:47,175
we are all by your side.

602
00:43:50,325 --> 00:43:51,626
Thank you.
